<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- whạʿysẖ lk .. ḥty̱ wlw krhwny ạlnạs
 whạkwn lk .. ḥty wlw ạsmy byndạs
 1- ḥty̱ wlw qạlwạ ʿny klạm .. ḥty̱ wlw ṣạdftny ạlậm
 hạfḍl ṣạmd fyk .. ạ̉nạ mtmsk byk
 hạfḍl ṣạmd fyk yạ yswʿ .. ạ̉nạ mtmsk byk
 ykfy ḥyạty ạ̹n ạ̹nt mʿạyạ .. hạrmy ạlʿạlm klh wrạyạ
 2- ḥty̱ wlw nsywạ ạlkẖlạn .. ạ̹ny ạ̉kẖwhm bʿdwạ kmạn
 hạrmy bḥmly ʿlyk .. wạṣrkẖ wạ̉nạ bnạdyk
 hạrmy bḥmly ʿlyk yạ yswʿ .. wạ̉ṣrkẖ wạ̉nạ bnạdyk
 ạ̹nt ạlkẖl ạlwfy dh kfạyẗ .. bạlqy̱ fy ḥbk lyã ḥmạyẗ
 3- gẖdr wmr wklh mnyn .. kẖạyf ạ̉qwlhạ ạ̹zạy kẖạynyn
 ʿlmny ạ̹zạy ạ̉sạmḥ .. wạnsy ạlḥrf ạljạrḥ
 ʿlmny ạ̹zạy ạ̉sạmḥ .. wạnsy ạlḥrf ạljạrḥ
 wạfḍl nạẓr lyk qdạmy .. wbḥbk rạḥ ạ̉ʿysẖ ạ̉yạmy</lyrics>
<title>whạʿysẖ lk</title>
